            <br/>
            Different categories of scientific software have different distribution requirements, limitations, and appropriate distribution channels, 
            which are defined in the Scientific <a href='https://www.osti.gov/stip/softwarecategories' target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Software Categories table</a>. 
